I want you to go downtown.

01:31:07.217 --> 01:31:08.176
Downtown?

01:31:08.885 --> 01:31:11.346
I want you to hit the ball into another zip code.

01:31:11.346 --> 01:31:13.348
[♪♪♪]

01:31:14.808 --> 01:31:17.435
Yes, sir.

01:31:18.853 --> 01:31:20.855
[CROWD CHEERING]

01:31:22.273 --> 01:31:24.234
This is it. Let's go.

01:31:24.234 --> 01:31:25.068
This is it!

01:31:29.948 --> 01:31:31.741
Gonna sacrifice?

01:31:31.741 --> 01:31:33.743
I told him to swing for the fence.

01:31:34.786 --> 01:31:37.288
- You did what?
- You heard me.

01:31:37.288 --> 01:31:40.166
You never tell a hitter to swing for the fence.

01:31:40.166 --> 01:31:41.668
I couldn't help myself.

01:31:47.090 --> 01:31:48.091
BOY:
Play ball!

01:31:50.427 --> 01:31:51.928
Strike!

01:31:51.928 --> 01:31:53.304
Come on, buddy.

01:31:54.806 --> 01:31:56.141
MAN:
Swing freeze.

01:31:58.184 --> 01:32:00.395
Come on. Come on, come on.

01:32:00.395 --> 01:32:02.647
Come on, buddy, hang in there.
Get the next one. Go.

01:32:04.607 --> 01:32:07.610
I got it! I got it! I got it!

01:32:07.610 --> 01:32:08.737
[HUFF LAUGHS]

01:32:11.406 --> 01:32:12.699
Good try. Good try.

01:32:14.200 --> 01:32:15.452
You can do this.

01:32:16.953 --> 01:32:19.539
You can do this. You can do this.

01:32:25.920 --> 01:32:26.921
It's gone.

01:32:26.921 --> 01:32:28.423
Come on, baby. Come on.

01:32:30.091 --> 01:32:31.718
It's gone!

01:32:34.220 --> 01:32:36.222
[♪♪♪]

