I'm not even a Red Sock.

01:33:46.167 --> 01:33:49.003
I am a damn Buzz.

01:33:51.339 --> 01:33:52.340
Thank you.

01:33:56.511 --> 01:33:57.887
Bumblebee.

01:33:57.887 --> 01:34:00.765
Yeah, that's what I am, a Buzz.

